This work explores batch training Bayesian Neural Networks using Graphics Processing Units. 

This work along with other results were presented in my dissertation: M. Perry, Bayesian Neural Networks in Data-Intensive
High Energy Physics Applications, http://diginole.lib.fsu.edu/islandora/object/fsu:185301/datastream/PDF/view


Note: 

To make with double precision:
make bin/BNN_ZZ DFLAG="-DHMC_DOUBLE "
